         <notesStmt>
            <note type="summary">1. Joy about birth of son. Brit Milah planned for
                            coming Thursday. 2. Apologies for not answering Z's earlier letter and
                            thanks for secret of the word. 2. About the examination of the woman
                            (cf. Livorno No. 22c and 24b). 3. Willing to assist R. Azriel ha-Kohen.
                            4. On the sale of scrolls and writings of R. Moses Miza.</note>
